{"tid":2314334,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"突發！印度衛生部長接種武肺疫苗 2周後竟宣布確診","createTime":"2020-12-06T12:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-06T13:19:49.000Z","uid":32511,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d87cfe23ed194b4173efae317fe73f1f4e812a7c","tid":2314334,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:53:45.000Z","msg":"打了武漢肺炎疫苗卻又染疫究竟是怎麼回事？印度哈里亞納邦（Haryana）內政部兼衛生<br />\n部部長維吉（Anil Vij），11月20日接種武漢肺炎疫苗，但卻在昨（5日）發文表示自己<br />\n確診了武漢肺炎（COVID-19，亦稱新冠肺炎）。對此，疫苗廠商澄清，疫苗分成2劑注射<br />\n，且效性要等第2劑注射後14天才能顯現，而維吉確診前只注射一劑。<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎自去年12月從中國發跡，至今在全球仍持續肆虐，日前有傳出疫苗已經問世，但<br />\n卻有印度官員在施打疫苗後反而確診。印度哈里亞納邦內政部兼衛生部部長維吉，昨天在<br />\n推特發文表示自己確診武漢肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ebc.net.tw/news/world/239442\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ebc.net.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2F239442&d=PkQR3zmsNSOm8whbchxq2jMRYSN2ZvgGkER1Jhb0l7M%3D&h=281c52e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ebc.net.tw/news/world/239442</a>"},{"pid":"4344e3f69928466d7522903340bcef32c0582942","tid":2314334,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85adb92ab36ead5be2f82bb05ebda719b57468e9","tid":2314334,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d3feac7f181ffb414f108e860d1d54a2ba0f03","tid":2314334,"uid":151196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-06T12:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e339f92273846b8a1d31db6a10815fea848474b","tid":2314334,"uid":45518,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"